		<div id="i10h585k" class="s1" data-reactid=".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$SITE_HEADER.1.1.$i10h585k">
<p class="font_8">AKA can I unpack the process by which your choice to watch The Interview was really your unconscious decision to partake in the mass cultural US-based movement to defend a so-called &#8220;work of art&#8221; (that is in fact merely an abuse of social capital and political power structures, faced by two stoned White males) while holding shields splattered with the words &#8220;Freedom of speech!&#8221; when really, the shields should read &#8220;LONG LIVE WHITE SUPREMACY!&#8221; ???</p>
</div>
<p>Christine Kim<br />
Yellow Peril, NYU Spring 2015</p>
